{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5b6d4f2d79","title":"对薄一波关于修建福建铁路问题的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9b8229540f","index":0,"year":1952,"month":12,"day":23,"articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d54ab0cc80","name":"薄一波","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"eaa28ac350","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"薄一波，当时任政务院财政经济委员会副主任兼财政部部长。"},{"id":"a1bee29988","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"周，指周恩来。南厦路，指江西南昌至福建厦门的铁路。陈嘉庚，福建厦门人，爱国华侨领袖。当时任中央人民政府委员、华侨事务委员会委员。韶厦路，指广东韶关至福建厦门的铁路。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ca33250f24","type":"title","text":"对薄一波叫关于修建福建铁路问题的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"},{"id":"eaa28ac350","type":"paragraph","text":"周、薄：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"},{"id":"a1bee29988","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）照昨晚所议，以先修南厦路为宜；但时间应提早，请考惠能否于三年内修好，以利军事运输。（二）陈嘉庚时下月来京，可与之商豹韶厦路与南厦路之利害，将南厦路之军事经济理由告诉他，取得他同意。因此他的来信可以不复","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"},{"id":"a36d982661","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"},{"id":"d876f39371","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79"}],"page":{"id":"c480dea067","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"5b6d4f2d79","start":390,"end":390}}}},"__N_SSG":true}